parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the Anti-lock Braking System (ABS) can cause the wheels to lock up, leading to a loss of braking ability, increased stopping distance, and potential accidents.
symptoms: Loud thumping or grinding noise when brakes are applied
wheels lock up during brake application
vehicle backfires or almost stalls when slowing down and accelerating again.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt retractor can cause the seat belt to become loose, compromising the safety of the occupant in the event of an accident or sudden stop.
symptoms: the seat belt buckle fails to latch or unlatch
the seat belt retractor makes a loud noise or vibrates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat belt buckle can cause the seat belt to become loose or detached, compromising the safety of the occupant in the event of an accident or sudden stop.
symptoms: The seat belt buckle fails to latch or unlatch
the seat belt buckle breaks or cracks

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to stall or experience a dramatic loss of power, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: the vehicle experiences a dramatic loss of power

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tailgate latch can cause the tailgate to open unexpectedly while driving, potentially leading to loss of cargo, damage to the vehicle or trailer, and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: The tailgate opens unexpectedly while driving
the tailgate pops open while towing a trailer
the tailgate does not stay closed.
